OL,3,CAngry Ginge shares update after mum's
OL,4,Chouse on day of Soccer Aid
OL,6,FStreamer and I'm A Celeb winner Angry
OL,7,FGinge has revealed him mum's house
OL,8,Fburned down on the day he took part in
OL,9,FSoccer Aid for UNICEF.
OL,11,FThe content creator from Eccles in
OL,12,FSalford ` whose real name is Morgan
OL,13,FBurtwistle ` shared a video of himself
OL,14,Fin what appears to be a living room
OL,15,Fcovered in black soot, on his
OL,16,FInstagram story.
OL,18,FWearing a face mask and rubber gloves
OL,19,Fin the video, he said: "You wouldn't
OL,20,Fthink it but right now i'm in my mum's
OL,21,Fhouse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
