PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780563951
OL,3,CAngry Ginge shares update after mum's
OL,4,Chouse on day of Soccer Aid
OL,6,F"As you can tell, morning of Soccer
OL,7,FAid, I get a phone call. Mum's house
OL,8,Fhas burned down. This is what we're
OL,9,Fdealing with right now."
OL,11,FThe 24-year-old confirmed he would
OL,12,Fshare more updates soon, but said this
OL,13,F"isn't even the worst of it".
OL,15,FGinge - who has become one of the UK's
OL,16,Fmost popular streamers with his angry
OL,17,Frants about football and his beloved
OL,18,FManchester United - later thanked fans
OL,19,Ffor all the messages of support.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
