FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780563951
OL,3,CAngry Ginge shares update after mum's
OL,4,Chouse on day of Soccer Aid
OL,6,FThe YouTuber previously posted on his
OL,7,FInstagram story that he would not be
OL,8,Fdoing a live stream after England's
OL,9,Fwin at Soccer Aid on Sunday 31 May due
OL,10,Fto a "major family issue".
OL,12,FHe also took the video to clear up
OL,13,Fspeculation. He said: "Everyone is
OL,14,Fassuming or guessing someone has
OL,15,Fpassed away, they've not."
OL,17,FEngland beat the World XI 3-2 in the
OL,18,FSoccer Aid match, with Ginge picking
OL,19,Fup player of the match for his
OL,20,Fperformance for England, playing the
OL,21,Ffull 90 minutes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
