PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780563951
OL,3,CAngry Ginge shares update after mum's
OL,4,Chouse on day of Soccer Aid
OL,6,FHe played alongside football stars and
OL,7,Fother celebrities including Wayne
OL,8,FRooney, Jill Scott, Tom Hiddleston and
OL,9,FOlly Murs.
OL,11,FAdolescence star Owen Cooper - who is
OL,12,Ffrom Warrington - made history as
OL,13,FSoccer Aid's youngest ever player, at
OL,14,Fjust 16.
OL,16,FThe 20th annual Soccer Aid raised just
OL,17,Funder #16.5 million for humanitarian
OL,18,Fcharity UNICEF.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
